								<span class="bg-msu-deep-ocean/10 text-msu-main-color text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded">Undergraduate</span>
							</div>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								A four-year degree program that focuses on the scientific and technological aspects of food production, preservation, safety, and quality control.
							</p>
							<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
								<a href="#" class="text-msu-deep-ocean font-medium hover:underline flex items-center">
