						</div>
						<div class="p-6">
							<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
								<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-msu-deep-ocean">Diploma in Fisheries Technology Major in Fish Processing</h3>
								<span class="bg-msu-deep-ocean/10 text-msu-main-color text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded">Diploma</span>
							</div>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								A diploma-level program, but with a focus on fish processing technologies, including preservation, packaging, and value addition of fish and seafood products.
							</p>
							<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
								<a href="#" class="text-msu-deep-ocean font-medium hover:underline flex items-center">
									Learn More
									<svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
